OL,3,CGovernment acted unlawfully twice in
OL,4,Capproving climate plan, High Court
OL,5,Crules
OL,7,FFriends of the Earth and ClientEarth,
OL,8,Fand the Good Law Project, took joint
OL,9,Flegal action against the Department
OL,10,Ffor Energy Security and Net Zero over
OL,11,Fits decision to approve the Carbon
OL,12,FBudget Delivery Plan (CBDP) in March
OL,13,F2023.
OL,15,FThe plan outlines how the country will
OL,16,Fachieve targets set out in the sixth
OL,17,Fcarbon budget, which runs until 2037,
OL,18,Fas part of wider efforts to reach net
OL,19,Fzero by 2050.
