OL,5,Crules
OL,7,FThe ruling marks a second High Court
OL,8,Fvictory for the three groups against
OL,9,Fthe government over its climate
OL,10,Fpolicies.
OL,12,FIn 2022, a different judge ruled the
OL,13,FGovernment's Net Zero Strategy was
OL,14,Funlawful as ministers were not
OL,15,Fproperly briefed on how individual
OL,16,Fpolicies would help meet climate
OL,17,Ftargets set out in the sixth carbon
OL,18,Fbudget, as required by the 2008
OL,19,FClimate Change Act (CCA).
