OL,5,Crules
OL,7,FIn the CBDP case, the groups claimed
OL,8,Fthat Mr Shapps had no or inaccurate
OL,9,Finformation from different government
OL,10,Fdepartments about the risks related to
OL,11,Fenacting climate policies under the
OL,12,Fplan, which gave a "misleading
OL,13,Fsummary" of whether they could be put
OL,14,Fin place.
