OL,5,Crules
OL,7,FDavid Wolfe KC, representing FoE, told
OL,8,Fthe court that some "risk tables" `
OL,9,Fused to demonstrate the risks
OL,10,Fassociated with delivering each policy
OL,11,F` were "recast" to remove information
OL,12,Fabout whether plans could be
OL,13,Fimplemented.
OL,15,FThe tables were not shared with
OL,16,FParliament, climate bodies or the
OL,17,Fpublic, meaning the plan could not be
OL,18,Fproperly scrutinised, the court heard.
