OL,7,FLawyers for the government said that
OL,8,FMr Shapps had "sufficient information"
OL,9,Fwhich "rationally supported" his
OL,10,Fdecision.
OL,12,FBut in his 50-page ruling, Mr Justice
OL,13,FSheldon said that the minister "could
OL,14,Fnot evaluate for himself" which
OL,15,Fpolicies in the CBDP would fail and
OL,16,Fwhich would be delivered based on the
OL,17,Finformation provided.
