OL,10,F"sufficient" information on whether
OL,11,Fthe plan should be approved.
OL,13,FIn response to the decision, a DESNZ
OL,14,Fspokesperson said: "The UK can be
OL,15,Fhugely proud of its record on climate
OL,16,Fchange.
