OL,7,F"Not only are we the first major
OL,8,Feconomy to reach halfway to net zero,
OL,9,Fwe have also set out more detail than
OL,10,Fany other G20 country on how we will
OL,11,Freach our ambitious carbon budgets.
OL,13,F"The claims in this case were largely
OL,14,Fabout process and the judgment
OL,15,Fcontains no criticism of the detailed
OL,16,Fplans we have in place. We do not
OL,17,Fbelieve a court case about process
OL,18,Frepresents the best way of driving
OL,19,Fprogress towards our shared goal of
OL,20,Freaching net zero."
